const enDescription = 'DigitalOcean Gradient AI review: H100/H200 GPU inference from $2.16/hr, serverless endpoints from $0.0005/1K tokens, 14 hosted models, June 3 OpenRouter integration. Compared to RunPod, CoreWeave, SambaNova.';
